{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_277b437c3ffe5n8oKk7kMHeudS","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d884c04e8001dMgCbKGwuRqu3n","parts":[{"id":"prt_d884c0ba7001rMzqXQ5WNLJbxt","messageID":"msg_d884c04e8001dMgCbKGwuRqu3n","sessionID":"ses_277b437c3ffe5n8oKk7kMHeudS","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_86dc558b6dce44faa1d239ef","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/workspace/docs/README.md"},"output":"<path>/workspace/docs/README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>1: # Django-LFS Documentation\n2: \n3: This directory contains the Sphinx-based documentation for django-lfs.\n4: \n5: ## Quick Start\n6: \n7: ### Install Dependencies\n8: \n9: ```bash\n10: # Install required packages\n11: make install\n12: # or\n13: pip install -r requirements.txt\n14: ```\n15: \n16: ### Build Documentation\n17: \n18: ```bash\n19: # Build HTML documentation\n20: make html\n21: \n22: # Or use the Python script\n23: python3 build_docs.py\n24: ```\n25: \n26: The built documentation will be available in `_build/html/index.html`.\n27: \n28: ## Available Commands\n29: \n30: - `make help` - Show all available commands\n31: - `make install` - Install required dependencies\n32: - `make html` - Build HTML documentation\n33: - `make clean` - Clean build directory\n34: - `make spelling` - Check spelling (requires enchant library)\n35: - `make linkcheck` - Check external links\n36: \n37: ## Requirements\n38: \n39: - Python 3.7+\n40: - Sphinx 7.0+\n41: - sphinx-rtd-theme (optional, for modern theme)\n42: - sphinxcontrib-spelling (optional, for spell checking)\n43: \n44: ## Theme\n45: \n46: The documentation uses a custom theme (`lfstheme`) with fallback to `sphinx-rtd-theme` if available. The custom theme is located in the `lfstheme/` directory.\n47: \n48: ## Structure\n49: \n50: - `conf.py` - Sphinx configuration\n51: - `index.rst` - Main documentation index\n52: - `requirements.txt` - Python dependencies\n53: - `Makefile` - Build commands\n54: - `build_docs.py` - Python build script\n55: - `_static/` - Static files (CSS, images)\n56: - `lfstheme/` - Custom theme files\n\n(End of file - total 56 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Django-LFS Documentation\n\nThis directory contains the Sphinx-based documentation for django-lfs.\n\n## Quick Start\n\n### Install Dependencies\n\n```bash\n# Install required packages\nmake install\n# or\npip install -r requirements.txt\n```\n\n### Build Documentation\n\n```bash\n# Build HTML documentation\nmake html","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"docs/README.md","time":{"start":1776108178630,"end":1776108178637}}}]}
